{"tid":823582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"個個屌曬鬼，但係照返工","createTime":"2018-09-16T23:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T23:56:24.000Z","uid":146580,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"63884028722d03325ee9bb62d3ba771b87fb7197","tid":823582,"uid":146580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T23:54:31.000Z","msg":"香港人，係咪有人拎住把槍指住你返工？<br />\n到左今時今日，你仲相信個垃圾政府有得救？<br />\n個個都係咁，唔通你又跟住咁？<br />\n返工姐唔洗搵條命博阿？<br />\n唉，雖然我都知道有部分人係手停口停<br />\n但係，當你知道個社會病態到咁既時候<br />\n你係咪仲繼續病落去？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人，幾時先識醒阿？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，幾時先識反抗？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我真係好灰，因為淨係識上連登叫春而做唔到任何野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"e4d0b45c09eaf802b941a7d6747ee635b8b16936","tid":823582,"uid":158585,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T23:55:39.000Z","msg":"番到公司未"},{"pid":"8ccc3a463a68b5b5dc21e6d2bf24ca9af0c93331","tid":823582,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T23:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做得政府狗官 驚閪你屌鳩佢咩  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鍵盤港豬 唔係以為自己打幾隻字會好有威力呀 ?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 團結 ? 咩嚟"},{"pid":"06994455bf4e85e70336d3d6481bfbaa672d622e","tid":823582,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T23:56:24.000Z","msg":"你都識講手停口停啦<br />\n咁重反抗啲咩"}]}